<TEXT>
SUTCLIFFE Speakman, the activated carbon company which had to be rescued by
shareholders after it ran into financial difficulties last year, reported an
interim pre-tax loss of Pounds 1.79m for the six months to September 30.
The result compared with a deficit of Pounds 11.18m in the nine months ended
December 30 1990.
The loss, which came on turnover of Pounds 15.4m (Pounds 38.9m), included
