<TEXT>
WILLMOTT DIXON companies have won contracts worth in excess of Pounds 40m.
Willmott Dixon Symes has been awarded contracts valued at Pounds 11.7m. They
are: a Pounds 2.4m contract at Hammersmith Hospital for a PACS x-ray unit; a
Pounds 5.6m extension and refurbishment to 105 Piccadilly, London W1, a
Grade II listed building, for Haslemere Estates; and a Pounds 2.7m library
