Parmiter Street, London E2.
Other new contracts being carried out from the company's Bedfordshire
headquarters are: a Pounds 2.2m contract for flats and houses for Notting
Hill Housing Trust at Uxbridge Road, Southall and a Pounds 1.6m scheme for
Network Housing Association in Willesden.
