and build houses and flats for Samuel Lewis Housing Trust in New Romney,
Kent; a Pounds 732,000 block of flats for Threshold Housing Association at
Shipka Road, Balham; and a Pounds 676,000 contract for Chichester Dicoesan
Housing Association at Hove.
Willmott Dixon Design &amp; Build is currently working on three contracts valued
at more than Pounds 4m. They include a distribution depot, valued at Pounds
1.8m, for Franthom Property Limberty at Rochester and a Pounds 1.5m swimming
